main: ^And that's a wrap, folks! We did it! We battled our way through the gnome hordes and emerged victorious.
^I hope you enjoyed watching as much as I enjoyed playing this awesome FPS game. We faced some tough challenges, but we managed to overcome them all.
^Thanks for tuning in and being a part of this incredible journey. Don't forget to hit that follow button so you don't miss out on any future adventures.
^Until next time, keep gaming, stay awesome, and remember - gnomes may be small, but they sure are mighty!
